lead_paragraph: Former champion Caroline Wozniacki outlasted fourth-seeded Carla Suarez Navarro 7-6 (4), 4-6, 6-4 to advance to the Pan Pacific Open quarterfinals on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Former Champ Wozniacki Advances to Pan Pacific Quarterfinals
